data.description: PROBATE AUCTION! The online auction will be conducted on Saturday May 30th 2020, at 11:00 AM! The asking price is the starting bid. This property will be sold as is, where is, and is subject to confirmation by the Superior Court Buyers may submit proxy bids/ offers prior to Auction Day or bid at Live Online Auction on May 30th 2020 at 11:00 AM. Each bidder MUST PRE-REGISTER at KWProbateAuction.com. A signed Coronavirus Property Entry Advisory and Declaration (CAR Form PEAD) is required from anyone who will be entering the property. This property will be sold As-Is, where is. Seller selects services. 50/50 split on commission with final sale price. Broker & broker's agents do not represent or guarantee accuracy of the Sq. Ft. Bed/Bath count, lot size/dimensions, (un)permitted spaces, Unit Mix or other info concerning the conditions or features of the property.
